                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>The title of the work is written on fol. a, on the 
                           front cover and on the spine.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc>The internal number of the monastic library (ዝ 1/0 7 24-8-93) 
                           is written on <locus target="#1r">fol.  1r</locus>.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc>Stamp of the church on fols. 2v, 3r, 96r, 133r.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e4"><desc>Corrections written over erasures: e.g., 
                           fols. 7va, 46rb, 46va, 47va, 75rb. </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e5"><desc>Tamallas-sign in the shape of two perpendicular lines, indicating the place 
                           where the omission written interlineally or in the margin belongs: 
                           fols. 81rb, 83ra. </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e6"><desc>Omitted words written interlineally or in the margin: e.g., fols. 25rb, 79ra, 83va. 
                        </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e7"><desc> Omitted words written in the margin and indicated by a sign in the shape of a 
                           cross with loops and arrows: <locus target="#50ra">fol.  50ra</locus>. 
                        </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e8"><desc>Signs, in the shape of a cross with a loop at the end of each arm, are 
                           written in the margin: fols. 59v, 68r, 93v.</desc></item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
